### To Connect with your MongoDb Database
1. change MONGO_URI with your MongoDb cluter uri in .env file  

### Install dependencies
2. npm install

### To run backend server
3. npm run server 

### To run backend server
4. npm run client

### To run whole project
5. npm run dev

### Frontend Project Details
Backend server: http://127.0.0.1:3000
Routes
Home: http://127.0.0.1:3000/

### Backend Project Details
Backend server: http://127.0.0.1:5000
Routes:
[GET] /api/product
[POST] /api/product
req Body:
{
    "name": "books",
    "quantity": 1,
    "amount": 10,
}

[DELETE] /api/product/:id
uses _id from GET product api

[POST] /api/user/register
req Body:  
{
    "first_name": "abcd",
    "last_name": "abcd",
    "email": "abcd@gmail.com",
    "password": "abcd@abcd"
}

[POST] /api/user/register
{
    "email": "abcd@gmail.com",
    "password": "abcd@abcd"
}
